nt style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is polished and completed to every detail of its appearance.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">You will be attracted to this handset on first sight.</font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Perfect design with monolithic metal casing, glass back gradient color gorgeous\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/huawei/huawei-mate-30-pro-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The phone is designed with a unibody metal casing and a perfect 3D curved glass back.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The soft curves meticulously cut on the body of the device makes Mate 30 Pro look like a gem created by nature itself.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The trendy gradient color effects are subtly coordinated, making anyone want to own right from the first floor to meet.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">3D curved</font></font></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;OLED screen&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;overflows like &quot;waterfall&quot; for the ultimate visibility</font></font></span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">No one can deny Huawei&#39;s successes with screen designs and technologies.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In Mate 20 Pro, users have been extremely impressed with a stylish &quot;rabbit ears&quot; screen, thin bezels and elegant curves to the sides.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">And with the&nbsp;</font></font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Huawei Mate 30 Pro</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;, the screen part is more charming than ever with a very typical design style.</font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"The screen uses OLED technology\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/huawei/huawei-mate-30-pro-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Mate 30 Pro owns the trendy rabbit ears screen following the current trend to help optimize the display space.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The curved 3D glass on both sides is called the &quot;waterfall&quot; screen by Huawei, so that the display space is expanded more than ever.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With that, with the use of an OLED panel with Full HD resolution, every visual experience is almost perfect.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">You can enjoy watching movies, playing games with the highest image quality.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Professional 4-camera system for true, sharp images like dedicated cameras</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Huawei Mate 30 Pro</font></font></em>&nbsp;</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is equipped with a cluster of 4 rear cameras located in the circular modum.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With 40MP movie sensor, f / 1.8 aperture, 40MP super sensor lens, f / 1.6 aperture, 8MP telephoto lens, f / 2.4 aperture and 3D depth sensing sensor.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This lens has autofocus support and AIS (AI Huawei) stabilization support.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Thanks to that Mate 30 Pro for ability in extremely low light conditions with many modes such as super slow motion and super fast.</font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"4 camera system professional\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/huawei/huawei-mate-30-pro-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The front camera on Huawei Mate 30 Pro is a dual camera with 32MP main lens, f / 2.0 aperture and 3D depth sensor.</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ultimate performance with Kirin 990, all operations are smooth</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The Kirin family of chips for&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/mobile.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\">phones</a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is a line of chips created and developed by Huawei itself.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This allows phones from Huawei to own the processor chip that best suits them and best meets the requirements set by the manufacturer.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With the&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Mate 30 Pro</em><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;, the advantage of this home made chip is even more pronounced.</font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Ultimate performance with the powerful Kirin 985 chip, everything is smoother and faster\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/huawei/huawei-mate-30-pro-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"Ultimate performance with the powerful Kirin 990 chip\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The Huawei Mate 30 Pro</em><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is powered by the&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Kirin 990</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;processor&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This chip offers an extremely powerful performance, incredible fast processing speed and the ability to handle extremely complex multitasking operations.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Thanks to Kirin 990, the GPU and CPU performance of the machine is also significantly increased, and the power consumption is also reduced, reducing the burden on the battery.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, artificial intelligence is integrated on the machine to help manage resources better, ensuring still running fast