(25, 'Huawei P40 Pro', 21990000, 21990000, 'Recently, the famous Chinese giant Huawei always \"stirred\" the smartphone market with high-end flagship devices and impressive configurations. And one of the flagships it will launch in 2020 is the Huawei P40 Pro and Huawei P40 . In particular, P40 Pro is a smartphone with a large curved screen, powerful processor and ultra-high resolution camera.', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Huawei P40 Pro has a modern design with eye-catching ceramic coating, sharp 120Hz frequency screen</font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Huawei&nbsp;</font></font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">P40 Pro</font></font></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is considered&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/mobile/huawei.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genuine Huawei phones\">Huawei</a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;&#39;s latest flagship&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">in 2020, so this smart phone will have an eye-catching appearance.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The device has a square design, a sturdy metal frame, the back is covered with a ceramic layer that adds elegance to a high-end flagship.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Modern design with eye-catching ceramic coating\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/huawei/huawei-p40-pro-3_1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The Huawei&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">P40 Pro&#39;s screen covers almost the entire front of the device, with a size of about 6.58 inches and Full HD + resolution on an OLED color background.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In particular, the screen can run with a refresh rate of up to 90Hz, resulting in a more realistic and clearer picture.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: ju