(26, 'Huawei Nova 5T', 8490000, 8490000, 'Nova 5T is the latest smartphone launched by Huawei in September 2019. Huawei Nova 5T is a powerful configuration smartphone with Kirin 980 octa-core chip, 32mp selfie camera but extremely competitive price', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The Huawei Nova 5T uses a 6.26-inch IPS LCD screen with a FHD screen design&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Nova 5T</em></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;, Huawei equips this flagship with IPS screen technology, this screen technology has the ability to provide fresh image quality, excellent color reproduction.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Applying this technology to the 6.26-inch screen with FHD resolution promises to be a product with the best screen on the market today with 16.7 million colors, 96% color saturation.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"6.26 inch OLed screen with FHD resolution\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/huawei/dien-thoai-huawei-5t.jpg\" style=\"box-sizi