(31, 'Oppo Reno 3 Pro', 13990000, 13990000, 'The upgraded version of OPPO Reno 3 called OPPO Reno 3 Pro was officially launched by OPPO smartphone company in March 2020. With outstanding design, powerful performance and breakthrough camera, Reno 3 Pro promises to be an attractive smartphone for photography enthusiasts .', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Sleek design with durable tempered glass</font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">OPPO Reno 3 Pro has a modern, slim and light design with plastic material to elegance &amp; elegance for the device overall.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The machine is launched in three official colors: Midnight Black (black), Sky White (white), and Auroral Blue (blue) to suit your own personality.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Sleek design with durable tempered glass\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/oppo-reno-3-pro-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The back is slightly curved on both sides to help create a sense of comfort &amp; certainty when held in the hand.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In particular, the front is covered with Corning Gorilla Glass 5, which not only creates a shine but also protects the device from scratches &amp; external impacts.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">6.4-inch screen covers the front with the ultrasonic fingerprint sensor</font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">OPPO Reno 3 Pro attracts users with its advanced dual-hole-punch screen design.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This design allows Reno 3 Pro to have a large 6.4-inch screen with a thin bezel, encapsulated inside a small body &amp; fits in the handle.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The screen has Super AMOLED color background, FullHD + 2400x1080 resolution, and T&Uuml;V Rheinland certification to protect your eyes when viewing the screen in dark environments.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"6.4-inch screen covers the front with the ultrasonic fingerprint sensor\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/oppo-reno-3-pro-2_1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Another advanced technology present on OPPO Reno 3 Pro is the ultrasonic fingerprint sensor.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The fingerprint sensor is hidden by OPPO directly below the screen, so you can unlock it in just 0.34 seconds with one touch.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The anti-fingerprint system has also been upgraded to help enhance the security of the device.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&quot;Quartet&quot; of 64MP rear camera for sharp photos</font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The biggest highlight in Reno 3 Pro lies in the super camera &quot;quartet&quot; on the back.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This camera cluster consists of 4 lenses, respectively: a 64MP main camera with f / 1.7 aperture for wide-angle shooting;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">13MP secondary camera with f / 2.4 aperture for telephoto shooting;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">8MP f / 2.2 camera with super wide-angle shooting;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">and 2MP f / 2.4 camera with mono shooting.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, Super PD autofocus, night mode, Ultra Steady 2.0 video recording and many other imaging features are all available on OPPO Reno 3 Pro, giving you the best and clearest photos. sharpest.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"&quot;Quartet&quot; of 64MP rear camera for sharp photos\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/oppo-reno-3-pro-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In the perforated position on the screen is a selfie camera cluster with two lenses: a 44MP main camera with f / 2.4 aperture and a 2MP secondary camera with f / 2.4 aperture supporting bokeh photography.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Selfie quality is further enhanced with the Ultra Night mode via image processing and facial recognition algorithms, making the photo captivating.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Helio P95 processor with 8GB of RAM and ColorOS 7 operating system</font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">OPPO Reno 3 Pro runs highly configurable games &amp; performs multitasking smoothly thanks to the 8-core MediaTek Helio P95 processor, manufactured on 12nm process.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">It also has a cooling system, 8GB of RAM and up to 256GB of storage.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Along with the optimized F2FS file storage system, OPPO Reno 3 Pro will give you more storage space, which enhances the user experience.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Helio P95 processor with 8GB of RAM and ColorOS 7 operating system\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/oppo-reno-3-pro-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; paddin