-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"4025mAh battery capacity with VOOC 4.0 fast charging\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/oppo-reno-3-pro-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Comes with OPPO&#39;s proprietary VOOC 4.0 fast charging technology.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Reno 3 Pro can charge from 0% to full battery in just over 1 hour, reaching 67% within 30 minutes.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Fast charging technology is also guaranteed by Safe Fast-Charge T&Uuml;V Rheinland certification to help protect both batteries and devices during charging.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Own genuine OPPO Reno 3 Pro phone with many attractive promotions only available at CellphoneS</font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">To experience firsthand and own genuine OPPO Reno 3 Pro with many attractive promotions, go to the nearest CellphoneS