(32, 'Oppo Reno 2F', 6990000, 6990000, 'Oppo Reno 2F  along with Oppo Reno 2 and Reno 2Z are 3 mid-range smartphones belonging to the latest 2nd generation Reno product line that have just been launched. The phone still carries a special design style, is equipped with up to 4 rear cameras, large capacity battery and the cheapest price in the Reno line up to the present time.', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Oppo&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Reno 2F with fingerprint sensor under the screen and protected with&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Gorilla Glass 5</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Oppo Reno 2F has a large screen up to 6.53 inches with Full HD + resolution (2340 x 1080 pixels) and an aspect ratio of 19.5: 9.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The fingerprint sensor feature of the device has also integrated below the screen for you to manipulate more easily.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Along with that is the eye protection mode that helps minimize the eye strain condition of users after a long period of use.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Oppo Reno 2F with fingerprint sensor under the screen and protected with Gorilla Glass 5\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/Oppo-reno-2f-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, Oppo Reno 2F is also equipped with&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><a href=\"https://www.corning.com/gorillaglass/vn/vi/glass-types/gorilla-glass-5.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Gorilla Glass 5, which</span></a></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;helps your phone screen be 80% protected from being broken or scratched when dropped from a height of 1.6 meters. .</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Terrible configuration with Helio P70 chip, 8GB of RAM and 128GB storage capacity</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Oppo Reno 2F</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is equipped with a powerful configuration with a RAM capacity of up to 8GB, a large number in the current smartphone.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With such a large amount of RAM will give you the ability to run great multitasking.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The chip used by the device is&nbsp;</font></font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Mediatek-Helio-P70-SoC-Benchmarks-and-Specs.418196.0.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">MediaTek Helio P70</span></a></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Oppo Reno 2F is equipped with a huge configuration with 8GB of RAM and 128GB of storage\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/Oppo-reno-2f-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Besides,&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Reno 2F</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;has a large internal memory of up to 128GB for you to freely take selfies and videos without having to worry about the storage is full, annoying during use.</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Oppo Reno2 F has 4 rear cameras that support wide-angle photography</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In the rear camera department, the Oppo Reno 2F phone is equipped with a 4-camera system including a 48 MP Samsung GM1 sensor, a 8 MP wide-angle sensor with 119-degree viewing angle, and 2 additional 2 MP sensor cameras with New design filter for portrait photography.&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Oppo Reno 2F is equipped with 4 rear cameras, supporting wide-angle photography\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/Oppo-reno-2f-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Oppo Reno 2F</em><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;has a rear camera system with advanced features of the camera, including Ultra Night Mode 2.0 for low-light photography, but it has the limitation of not having EIS for video stabilization.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Modern features are also integrated on the camera such as: slow motion mode, gesture shooting, AI camera, etc.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Oppo Reno 2F has a 16 MP selfie camera designed in the form of pop-up</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Like Reno 2, the 16MP selfie camera of&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Oppo Reno2 F is</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;also designed to be hidden in the machine, not on the screen like other regular smartphones.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">However, the front camera uses a normal pop-up mechanism, not the &quot;shark fin&quot; type like on Reno 2.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"16 MP front camera is designed in Pop-up format\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/oppo/Oppo-reno-2f-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Front camera of Reno 2F Oppo also&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/mobile/oppo.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Oppo</a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;integrated modern features such as: photography remove fonts, AI beauty, face detection, auto focus, full HD video recording, ...</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Huge 4000 mAh battery capacity and support for VOOC 3.0 fast charging</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Demand for smartphone users is huge, so the manufacturer has equipped the&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\"><em style=\"b