; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">LCD&nbsp;</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;technology&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">and a pixel density of 403 ppi for extremely sharp, realistic displays.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With a total display area of ​​up to 81.37%, you can enjoy the perfect display space.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The screen is also equipped with Gorilla Glass toughened glass 3 to increase the durability of the screen, protect the screen from bumps, scratches better.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Realme 6 impressive performance with MediaTek Helio G90T + 4GB RAM and 128GB internal memory</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Despite being a cheap smartphone, Realme 6 still possesses powerful and impressive performance when equipped with MediaTek Helio G90T chip manufactured according to 12nm process along with&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/ARM-Mali-G76-MP4-GPU-Benchmarks-and-Specs.443046.0.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0