(34, 'Realme 6 Pro', 7990000, 7990000, 'Besides Realme 6,  Realme 6 Pro is also the latest Realme smartphone to be equipped with four impressive rear cameras that produce extremely sharp images with extremely high resolution. In addition, this phone also has increased performance and significant battery life.', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Realme 6 Pro has a luxurious monolithic plastic design, a large 6.6 inch Full HD screen</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With a significant increase in internal performance, the Realme 6 Pro exterior is also extremely luxurious.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Machine made from monolithic plastic creates a solid feel when holding.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Not too rough, the lines cut behind the back close to the palm of the hand.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Especially, the monolithic plastic material of the phone cover is high-class when viewed from the outside, feeling very luxurious and limiting fingerprints.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Luxury monolithic plastic design, large 6.4 inch Full HD screen\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/realme-6-pro-1_1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The remarkable point that makes up the beauty of&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Realme 6 Pro</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is the large screen size.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">It is equipped with a screen up to 6.6 inches Full HD resolution of 1080x2340 px.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">For extremely impressive pixel densities of up to 403 PPI on IPS LCD panels.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, the screen is also equipped with Corning Gorilla Glass 5 tempered glass with super ions to limit screen breakage.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Strong performance with Snapdragon 720G chip, 8GB RAM 128GB internal memory</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Realme 6 Pro is powered by&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Qualcomm Snapdragon 720G, which</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;is the second generation of the 700 series mobile gaming platform, uses 10% less power than the 10nm process.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Comes with 8GB RAM, 128GB internal memory to help improve performance significantly, run multitasking applications on the machine easily and meet all the needs of games, surfing the web or watching movies of users.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Strong performance with Snapdragon 730 chip, 6Gb Ram 64Gb internal memory\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/realme-6-pro-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The device is run on Android 10 operating system with a refreshed user interface that optimizes significantly speed.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition,&nbsp;</font></font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">Android 10</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;also brings improvements to the camera, multiple shooting modes and has a better level of security.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With Android 10,&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Realme 6 Pro</em><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;will bring you an extremely amazing experience.</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Realme 6 Pro has a battery of up to 4300mAh, built-in 30W fast charging</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With the perfect design of performance and appearance, battery and battery life are also important factors that affect the experience on Realme 6 Pro.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The 4300mAh battery capacity is the huge battery capacity in the current Realme series.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">You can comfortably use that for an entire day without worrying about running out of battery like other phones.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Battery capacity up to 4500mAh, equipped with VOOC fast charging\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/realme-6-pro-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Particularly impressive on the&nbsp;</font><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Realme 6 Pro</font></span></em></font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/mobile.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\">&nbsp;phone</a>&nbsp;<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">is the ability to charge&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Flash Charge 30W</font></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;fast&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This technology is announced by the company to give 20% faster speed than the previous version but still does not get hot,&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">capable of charging&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">from 0% to 100% battery in just 60 minutes.</font></span></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Equipped with 4 rear cameras that support ultra-wide angle shooting, 16MP + 8MP front camera</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The main highlight of Realme 6 Pro is that it is equipped with up to four rear cameras to ensure users can take beautiful and authentic photos easily.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The main camera has a resolution of 64MP, the secondary camera has a resolution of 12MP support for wide-angle shooting, the secondary camera with 8MP resolution supports image zoom and the secondary camera 2MP supports capturing fonts.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Equipped with 4 rear cameras that support ultra-wide angle shooting, 20MP front camera\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/realme-6-pro-3_1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Not only is it equipped with a high-end rear camera,&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">Realme 6 Pro is</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;also equipped with dual front cameras up to 16MP and 8MP that support extremely sharp selfie.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With Android 9.0 operating system the device supports many different shooting modes.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Bringing you into extremely interesting experiences.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Dual front cameras up to 16 MP and 8MP\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/realme-6-pro-2_1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: borde