(35, 'Realme 5s', 4990000, 4990000, 'n November 2019, Realme officially launched its low-priced phone called Realme 5s , which is also a slight upgrade on the camera, configuration and battery compared to the previous generation, the Realme 5. was released in August.', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Hard plastic design with luxurious crystal effect glass and a good grip feeling</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The design language on the Realme 5s is similar to that of its predecessor, the device has a back, a frame made of plastic that makes the device durable, not only that this part is also painted very fake glass. eye-catching, crystal-like effect creates a luxurious look for the device.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The device has three eye-catching color options that are blue, purple and red.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Hard plastic design with luxurious crystal effect glass and a good grip feeling\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/real-me-5s-4.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The feeling of holding this Realme 5s is also very strong, with reasonable rounded corners creating a pleasant feeling for users.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Not only that, but the size of this device is also very compact (164.4 x 75.6 x 9.3mm) along with the weight of 198g so that users will not feel uncomfortable when using the device in time. long and convenient to pocket, carry anywhere.&nbsp;</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4 camera system 48MP for sharp, brilliant, vivid images</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The difference of Realme 5s compared to the previous generation Realme 5 is that the rear camera system has been upgraded to 48MP main sensor.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The remaining three lenses include 1 8MP ultra-wide lens, f / 2.2;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">1 2MP, f / 2.4 macro lens together with 1 2MP, f / 2.4 depth lens.&nbsp;</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"4 camera system 48MP for sharp, brilliant, vivid images\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/real-me-5s-5.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In terms of photographic quality, the device produces very good quality in the price range.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With 4-pixel coupling mechanism, the device will produce images with impressive detail, brilliant, vivid but still very realistic.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Besides, Realme 5s is also equipped with a 13MP selfie camera with a font erase mode to help users have sparkling selfie photos to share with friends.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Stable configuration with&nbsp;</font></font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/sforum/qualcomm-ra-mat-snapdragon-665-11nm-snapdragon-730-va-730g-8nm-voi-nhieu-cai-tien\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=