izing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Along with that is 4GB of RAM and two options of 64GB / 128GB internal memory, SD memory card support for users to store data, photos, videos.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Stable configuration with Snapdragon 665 chip and smooth OS ColorOS 6\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/real-me-5s-3.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Realme 5s is also equipped with ColorOS 6, customized based on&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.android.com/versions/pie-9-0/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Operating system Android 9.0 (pie)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Android 9.0 Pie</font></span></a></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">ColorOS 6 brings a smooth experience for users, gestures are smooth.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">It also has some nice features like split screen, lots of battery saving options, Game Space to help prevent notifications when the user is playing the game.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">6.5 inch HD +</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.lenovo.com/ie/en/faqs/pc-life-faqs/what-is-an-ips-display/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IPS screen\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;IPS</font></span></a></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;LCD</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"https://www.lenovo.com/ie/en/faqs/pc-life-faqs/what-is-an-ips-display/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IPS screen\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;screen</font></span></a></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;with sensitive fingerprint sensor, high security</font></font></span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The Realme 5s is equipped with a large 6.5-inch IPS LCD panel that provides a large display space for users, especially for the elderly with poor eyesight.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The sharp HD + resolution (720 x 1600 pixels) will surely make users feel satisfied.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Besides, this screen is also protected by Gorilla Glass 3+ which will minimize scratches as well as minimize damage when the machine is struck.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"6.5 inch HD + IPS LCD screen with sensitive fingerprint sensor, high security\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/real-me-5s-1.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">On the back of the device is the place to place a one-touch fingerprint sensor, users just need to put their hands on and the