(36, 'Realme 3 Pro 6GB', 3990000, 3990000, 'Realme 3 Pro is a great Realme phone in the budget segment with powerful hardware and long usage time, meeting the needs of users who like to play games. Add to that beautiful design and fresh changes.', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Face&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">back&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">so curved S-shaped&nbsp;</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">color change SA&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">c unique</font></span></font></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The back of Realme 3 Pro is made from quality molded plastic combined with many different gradient color options for an eye-catching appearance.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">A special feature is the light effect above the gradient color layer with S-shaped curved lines, when you hold the camera in the sun, it will be very beautiful.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"S-shaped curved back panel changes color nicely\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/Realme-3-Pro-6GB-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With the ability to change colors very nicely, users will have different colors depending on the angle of different eyes.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">M&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Criminal 6.3 inch Full HD + resolution&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ratio 19.5: 9</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The Realme 3 Pro has a 6.3-inch screen, with a 19.5: 9 aspect ratio.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Besides, the screen is overflowing with a drop of water on the top.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This type of screen design will help users have a more comfortable and spacious experience.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"6.3 inch screen with Full HD + resolution, 19.5: 9 aspect ratio\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/Realme-3-Pro-6GB-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The glass is equipped with a toughened Gorilla Glass layer to help protect the glass better.&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/mobile.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\">The phone</a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;uses&nbsp;</font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">IPS LCD panel</font></font></span></span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;with Full HD + 1080 x 2340 px resolution for very good visibility, natural harmonious colors</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Snapdragon 710 Snapdragon&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">energy saving 30% - 6GB RAM</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The performance of Realme 3 Pro has been significantly improved with the 64-bit Snapdragon 710 octa-core processor.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The advantage of this chip is the ability to save 30% more energy than the Snapdragon 660 equipped on the older generation.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"The Snapdragon 710 chip saves 30% power - 6GB RAM\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/Realme-3-Pro-6GB-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The RAM of the device is up to 6 GB, equivalent to the 2019 flagships. So Realme 3 Pro can completely handle smoothly and smoothly all basic tasks such as web browsing, watching high-resolution movies or adjusting. retouch photos.</font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">P&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">in capacity 4.045 mAh VOOC 3.0 fast charging technology with two SIM slots</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Realme 3 Pro has a battery capacity of 4,045 mAh, supports fast charging technology VOOC 3.0 20W will quickly in just 30 minutes for 75% of the battery is charged into the machine.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The included charger allows charging at 20W.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"4.045 mAh battery with VOOC 3.0 fast charging technology with dual SIM slots\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/Realme-3-Pro-6GB-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The Realme 3 Pro also has an FM radio, Bluetooth 5.0, a 3.5mm headphone port, a dedicated microSD card slot and two SIM slots.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Instead of switching to USB-C as other manufacturers have done, Realme 3 Pro is only equipped with&nbsp;</font></font><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">micro-USB</span><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;port&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">.</font></font></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Stand Pie Android 9.0 interface 6.0 ColorOS</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Realme 3 Pro runs on Android 9.0 Pie OS ColorOS 6.0 interface with some significant changes.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">One of the most important changes is that Relme has used a more modern design than previous versions that made the overall interface more beautiful.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65); font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Operating system Android 9.0 Pie Interface ColorOS 6.0\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/realme/Realme-3-Pro-6GB-5.jpg\" style=\"box-siz