(38, 'POCO F2 PRO(6GB - 128GB)', 12990000, 12990000, 'POCO F2 Pro phone - Smartphone owns a quad camera after professional photography', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Metal rim design, luxurious glass back and 6.67 inch screen</span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65);\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The smartphone POCO F2 Pro is considered to be a phone with a high-class and luxurious appearance thanks to the edge made of sturdy and eye-catching metal material.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Back machine is made of glass bearing should bring a sense of luxury and a lot more attractive.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65);\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Metal rim design, luxurious glass back and 6.67 inch screen\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/xiaomi/poco-f2-pro-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65);\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, the screen of POCO F2 Pro has a size of 6.67 inches, accounting for 92.7% of the body area, so that all images are displayed with a wider viewing angle and more comfortable.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The screen is also equipped with HDR + technology and Full HD + resolution, giving users every detail with sharpness and high realism.</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65);\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Many color versions\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/xiaomi/poco-f2-pro-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Cluster 4 rear cameras with 64MP main camera and 20MP selfie camera &quot;peek&quot; modern</span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.35; color: rgb(10, 38, 60); font-size: 16px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(60, 61, 65);\">\r\n	<font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The most impressive highlight of&nbsp;</font><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/mobile.html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genuine phone\">the</a><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"box-sizi